## Dungeons — not player-facing yet

`/dungeons` shows “Will come later”. Gated by keys/quests when shipped.

## Field encounters (`events.json`)

Standalone tavern tab — **not** mission board contracts.

## When editing

- User-facing → bump `APP_VERSION`.
- New mission/interlude content → edit bible, run `node scripts/import-mission-bible.mjs`.
- Keep stable `id` values (mission slugs without `mis_` prefix; interludes keep `evt_*` ids).
- Combat monsters: IDs from `game-data/dungeons.json` → `monsters[]`.
